{"title":"Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.013Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境","updated":"2023-07-28T08:55:39.146Z","content":"<h2 id=\"linux下从零配置hadoop环境\">Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境<a title=\"#linux下从零配置hadoop环境\" href=\"#linux下从零配置hadoop环境\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>一、必要准备</strong><br>\n1、一个装好Linux系统的虚拟机<br>\n2、Oracle JDK安装包<br>\n3、Hadoop程序包</p>\n<p><strong>二、操作步骤</strong><br>\n1、首先安装oracle jdk，具体步骤可以<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/114478601\" target=\"_blank\">参考这里</a><br>\n确保输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">java <span class=\"literal\">--version</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>有java版本提示<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402203003900.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n2、安装hadoop<br>\n首先下载hadoop包，我这里是3.1.4版本<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402203049746.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n解压到本地<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402203122207.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n然后配置hadoop环境<br>\n在<strong>hadoop安装目录</strong>下，输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> etc/hadoop</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo vi hadoop<span class=\"literal\">-env</span>.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>把刚刚的jdk地址加进去，加个java_home就行了<br>\n然后按下<code>esc</code>，输入  <code>:wq</code>  退出<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402203517802.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n此时，在当前目录下，输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./bin/hadoop version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>就会弹出hadoop版本信息<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402203743221.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"linux修改用户中文文件夹为英文","link":"2023/07/28/linux修改用户中文文件夹为英文"},"next":{"title":"linux下切换系统默认python版本","link":"2023/07/28/linux下切换系统默认python版本"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境/","toc":[{"id":"linux下从零配置hadoop环境","title":"Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"296 字约 2 分钟"}